data.title: Interrupted Program by RUGRATS (Looney Moon Records)

data.text:
published on 2021-07-09T06:44:30Z

After a few months of hibernation, Rugrats are the frontliners of the awakening of Looney Moon Records as the label's producers were busy in their studio. The Swiss duo is back in the spotlight today with their new EP "Twisted", including 2 solo tracks and a featured collaboration with Mowgli. An explosion of high frequencies that is going to set up your minds for your next dance-floor experience. Stretch your synapses before the Rugrats get them twisted!

Genre

Psytrance
